{"tid":680584,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體回憶]講下陪住大家成長既街機GAME","createTime":"2018-05-27T09:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T10:01:04.000Z","uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da17f0e63644ce73a53f85e266481cd387b8d039","tid":680584,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"去機舖打機應該係好多70,80,90後都有做過既事(00後太幸福,電腦同PS係當時已經普及),當年既Game係唔少人心目中已經成為左經典,而家就細數下呢D經典街機GAME<br />\n<br />\n益智考反應系列<br />\nPac-Man(食鬼)<br />\n可以算係最初代既街機遊戲,經典中嘅經典,考驗玩家頭腦同反應<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/365995/org/2146c003b1d9081057f0d6d4e3ff1ad2.gif/kWaXI2_iRBl9QowybMnnPMQ8bP2IE9jynRkg1J0ZINQ?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F365995%2Forg%2F2146c003b1d9081057f0d6d4e3ff1ad2.gif%2FkWaXI2_iRBl9QowybMnnPMQ8bP2IE9jynRkg1J0ZINQ%3Fv%3Dw640&h=cb1bf12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPhoto Hunt----EZ touch 入面其中一款既touch screen 遊戲,從左,右2幅圖中找出錯處,由於玩法簡單,而且普遍只需$1,所以最啱用黎等人消時間玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/photohunt_8838815105a21361484441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fphotohunt_8838815105a21361484441.jpg&h=b4e1fedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打飛機系列<br />\n1941 Counter Attack ---經典垂直打飛機game,以第2 次世界大戰為背景<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.game-oldies.com/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/titles/capcom-cps-1/1941.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.game-oldies.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2Ftitles%2Fcapcom-cps-1%2F1941.png&h=3529ee33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStriker 1945---另一款經典垂直打飛機game<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.horace.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/s1945ii-210x300.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.horace.org%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2Fs1945ii-210x300.png&h=a6846aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動作系列<br />\n吞食天地II 赤壁之戰---以三國演義中博望坡之戰到赤壁之戰為劇本,每關打贏敵人Boss之後果句敵將is doctor lee!同版與版之間鬥快撳制食雞脾最為人熟識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2sf6lk1/432s0001r822p2por60q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2sf6lk1%2F432s0001r822p2por60q.jpg&h=490c500f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFinal Fight系列---遊戲概念源自Capcom另一經典Street Fighter,但玩法由格鬥變成橫向動作<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.share.photo.xuite.net/hsiang282/1a2e992/9529588/417760926_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fhsiang282%2F1a2e992%2F9529588%2F417760926_m.jpg&h=cb3c94eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐龍快打---最多可以三個人同時合作,遊戲有大量槍械彈藥可以用既橫向動作game,其中可以揸車果一關最深入民心<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/klkd2-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fklkd2-1024x576.jpg&h=b7a62015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSpike Out---可以算係開創3D動作game既先河,最多可以4人同時合作過關<br />\n<img src=\"https://segaretro.org/images/f/f7/Spikeout_DBO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsegaretro.org%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff7%2FSpikeout_DBO.png&h=44bb43fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n格鬥系列<br />\n街頭霸王(Street Fighter)系列---如果講機舖打機唔講街霸,不如唔好講...無人不識既經典格鬥遊戲,其中第二代(Street Fighter II)可以話係最有代表性,席席BIRD極,all u get ,阿力cool等角色必殺技叫聲洗盡各人腦,而「屈機」一詞極有可能就係出自街霸<br />\n<img src=\"https://2af5c8302d6ffd665a70-998b2bffaa4ef0fca90771004190a4a2.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/screenshot-street-fighter-2-ce-game.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2af5c8302d6ffd665a70-998b2bffaa4ef0fca90771004190a4a2.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com%2Fscreenshot-street-fighter-2-ce-game.jpg&h=181d34e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe King of Fighters拳皇系列---90年代尾至千禧年代同Street Fighter係格鬥game上分庭抗禮,可謂一時瑜亮,開創三打三團隊格鬥模式,其中以KOF 97,98最受歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.fightersgeneration.com/games/kof98selectf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fightersgeneration.com%2Fgames%2Fkof98selectf.jpg&h=37cd9899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVirtual-On---可以話係機械人對戰既始祖,仿駕駛倉設計座位及雙搖桿操控設計令玩家更有真實感,但由於可能Virtual-On既操控太過另類,令玩家對其評價十分兩極化<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SoUGqhPQFI0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FSoUGqhPQFI0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f9f0baa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGUNDAM VS系列--由初代連邦vs.自護DX到GUNDAM SEED DESTINY vs.Z.A.F.T既高達格鬥遊戲,最多可供4人同時玩,以2對2形式對戰,初代連邦vs.自護節奏較慢,到後來奧干vs.泰坦斯及GUNDAM SEED DESTINY vs.Z.A.F.T.加入可變型機種及覺醒系統令節奏加快<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamefaqs.akamaized.net/screens/d/b/c/gfs_83565_2_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamefaqs.akamaized.net%2Fscreens%2Fd%2Fb%2Fc%2Fgfs_83565_2_3.jpg&h=30e1bd6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一身射擊系列<br />\nTime Crisis系列---可以話係最成功既第一身射擊game,首創踩腳踏避子彈既設計,加上支槍有少少後座力,有D開真槍既感覺<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.arcadeguns.com/images/games/mame-timecris.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.arcadeguns.com%2Fimages%2Fgames%2Fmame-timecris.jpg&h=f69f834b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n體育系列<br />\nVirtua Striker系列---由初代一味屈底線傳中都到後來Virtua Striker 4有得加速,有得半場換人,有得用卡save低進度,開隱藏球員同升稱號,變化大左<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sega-mag.com/jeux/Arcade/380/3802008013092755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sega-mag.com%2Fjeux%2FArcade%2F380%2F3802008013092755.jpg&h=4777919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVirtua NBA---一隻一味屈3分既籃球game(連O'neal都射到3分,WTF)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.arcade-museum.com/images/118/11812421856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arcade-museum.com%2Fimages%2F118%2F11812421856.jpg&h=6d157b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVirtua Tennis系列---可以同Virtua Striker,Virtua NBA合稱Virtua 體育三寶,以真實球員及球速快為賣點,第三代Virtua Tennis 3更可以開卡 save低進度<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/d5WlRxDe22c/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd5WlRxDe22c%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=c5d9f1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWinning Eleven系列---以家用版為藍本,用卡玩可以靠贏波儲分既方式去買人增強自己隊波既實力,更可聯線同係香港其他機舖甚至遠在日本既人一決高下<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.playright.dk/object/066/652/1287-world-soccer-winning-eleven-arcade-championship-2012@800x600min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.playright.dk%2Fobject%2F066%2F652%2F1287-world-soccer-winning-eleven-arcade-championship-2012%40800x600min.jpg&h=74303a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽車系列<br />\n頭文字D系列---極受歡迎既賽車game,因比賽多跑山路,技術要求較高<br />\n<img src=\"https://sloanwang.files.wordpress.com/2011/06/idv3_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsloanwang.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F06%2Fidv3_a.jpg&h=ff9928a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣岸Midnight系列---同頭文字D齊名之作,因比賽多跑公路,速度感較頭D強<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRIEOhz7WoMTeE9yUGtfTQRwMT9qxXPmB0dZMNCK80bMfi3-5395g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRIEOhz7WoMTeE9yUGtfTQRwMT9qxXPmB0dZMNCK80bMfi3-5395g&h=4b6073f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n音樂系列<br />\nDance Dance Revolution(DDR)---俗稱跳舞機,其影響力甚廣,當中歌曲butterfly,barbie girl更風靡一時,當時吸引無數少男少女玩,甚至跳舞高手上去showoff,引來眾多人圍觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1xgbJlhVp8Y/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1xgbJlhVp8Y%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=3c646d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBeatmania---俗稱捽碟機,既要捽碟,又要按那五個掣,難度不少,人人都捽到好似DJ Tommy上身咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nm_fb_beatmania_feature_35141483359edd2fe2b6a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnm_fb_beatmania_feature_35141483359edd2fe2b6a9.png&h=affb9659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDrummania---俗稱打鼓機,當時音樂game大熱,佢同DDR,加上Beatmania,令機舖一時間變成音樂中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/564x/54/92/4f/54924fb310703ab6b2b6f93a615dc66a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F54%2F92%2F4f%2F54924fb310703ab6b2b6f93a615dc66a.jpg&h=11d0150b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太鼓之達人---畫面得意可愛既打鼓Game<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8qMF7O6tcYA/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F8qMF7O6tcYA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7f1f798e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97a9b50c131467decda7d7371b940a6701a41a6","tid":680584,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"育成系列<br />\nG1 Leading Sire---俗稱跑馬機,用卡可以自己育成馬匹訓練出賽<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.arthurkok.net/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/08/08152009230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.arthurkok.net%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2009%2F08%2F08152009230.jpg&h=a6b9bad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niHorse Racing---港版跑馬機,玩法同G1 Leading Sire差唔多以全中文作賣點,增加歸屬感<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cuhkacs.org/~henryporter/Bo-Blog/attachment/1188379580_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuhkacs.org%2F~henryporter%2FBo-Blog%2Fattachment%2F1188379580_0.jpg&h=b47c95ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國志大戰---以三國時代為背景的線上街機對戰交換卡片遊戲.有別於一般常見的街機遊戲,此遊戲以實體卡片做為控制媒介,玩家在機台上移動卡片來進行遊戲.玩家可以使用不同的武將卡攻略對方城池擊敗對手。<br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/x0526zhp8t1_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fx0526zhp8t1_496_280%2F0&h=2d9da5ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55c0d884b93265c2d04ff56dc74e39f4c8aee244","tid":680584,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/174658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F174658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a886d272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/174702_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F174702_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=81ff0213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dafd72e80914eaf8a3e085446339003560f46100","tid":680584,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"Seed"},{"pid":"a1e6193c0d8f4cc737345f9bff4af4863c768674","tid":680584,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"無敵將is doctor Lee?"},{"pid":"13135982c675de417c82ec0cf9c75864719752aa","tid":680584,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1e6193c0d8f4cc737345f9bff4af4863c768674","tid":680584,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"無敵將is doctor Lee?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"你睇真D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}